'''基礎物理學突破獎'''（{{lang-en|Breakthrough Prize in Fundamental Physics}}）是[[突破奖|突破奖]]其中一項，由[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]]企業家[[尤里·米尔纳|尤里·米尔纳]]於2012設立的基礎物理學獎基金會（Fundamental Physics Prize Foundation）頒發，用以獎勵在[[物理學|基礎物理學]]有重大成就的[[物理學|物理學]]家<ref name="launch">{{cite press release |url=https://breakthroughprize.org/News/15 |title=New annual US$3 million Fundamental Physics Prize recognizes transformative advances in the field |date=2012-07-31 |accessdate=2015-11-19 |publisher=[[突破奖|突破奖]] |archive-date=2015-11-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151119100208/https://breakthroughprize.org/News/15 |language=en}}</ref>，尤其是較近期的發現和成就<ref>{{cite news |author1=Sample, Ian |title=Biggest science prize takes web tycoon from social networks to string theory |url=https://www.theguardian.com/science/2012/jul/31/prize-science-yuri-milner-awards |accessdate=2022-05-01 |work=[[衛報|衛報]] |date=2012-07-31 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20220501051733/https://www.theguardian.com/science/2012/jul/31/prize-science-yuri-milner-awards |archivedate=2022-05-01 |language=en}}</ref>。不同領域的物理學家，包括[[理論物理學|理論物理學]]、[[數學物理|數學物理學]]和[[實驗物理學|實驗物理學]]，均可得獎<ref>{{cite web |title=Fundamental Physics |url=https://breakthroughprize.org/Prize/1 |publisher=基礎物理學突破獎 |accessdate=2022-04-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20220429024006/https://breakthroughprize.org/Prize/1 |archivedate=2022-04-29 |language=en}}</ref>。基礎物理學突破獎於2012年開始頒發，每一位獲獎者都可獨得獎金300萬[[美元|美元]]<ref name="launch"/><ref>{{cite news |author1=Wall, Mike |title=Pioneering gravity research snags $3 million physics Breakthrough Prize |url=https://www.space.com/breakthrough-prize-fundamental-physics-gravity.html |accessdate=2022-05-03 |work=Space.com |publisher=[[未來出版社|未來出版社]] |date=2020-09-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20220503081422/https://www.space.com/breakthrough-prize-fundamental-physics-gravity.html |archivedate=2022-05-03 |language=en |quote=... Four $3 million Breakthrough awards were granted this year in the life sciences, one in mathematics and two in fundamental physics ...}}</ref>，是迄今獎金最高的物理學獎項<ref name>{{cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2012/07/31/science/9-scientists-win-yuri-milners-fundamental-physics-prize.html?_r=1 |title=9 Scientists Receive a New Physics Prize |publisher=[[紐約時報|紐約時報]] |date=2012-07-31 |accessdate=2012-08-04 |archive-date=2012-08-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120803001610/http://www.nytimes.com/2012/07/31/science/9-scientists-win-yuri-milners-fundamental-physics-prize.html?_r=1 |language=en}}</ref>。

== 特別獎、新视野物理奖和物理前沿奖 ==
基礎物理學突破獎另設特別獎、新视野物理奖和物理前沿奖。跟基礎物理學突破獎不同，特別獎並不限於近期的發現和貢獻，但金額同樣是300萬[[美元|美元]]<ref>{{cite press release |url=https://breakthroughprize.org/News/32 |title=Special Breakthrough Prize In Fundamental Physics Awarded For Detection Of Gravitational Waves 100 Years After Albert Einstein Predicted Their Existence |date=2016-05-02 |accessdate=2022-04-30 |publisher=突破奖 |location=[[三藩市|三藩市]] |archive-date=2022-04-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220430141207/https://breakthroughprize.org/News/32 |language=en}}</ref>。新视野物理奖則由2013年開始頒發，授予有潛質的年輕[[物理學|物理學]]研究者；每位得獎者可獲10萬美元<ref>{{cite news |title=Alan Guth wins $3 million Fundamental Physics Prize |url=https://news.mit.edu/2012/alan-guth-wins-fundamental-physics-prize-0731 |accessdate=2022-04-30 |publisher=[[麻省理工學院|麻省理工學院]] |date=2012-07-31 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20220430140602/https://news.mit.edu/2012/alan-guth-wins-fundamental-physics-prize-0731 |archivedate=2022-04-30 |language=en}}</ref>。物理前沿奖截至目前只頒發過2屆，得獎者會自動被提名下屆基礎物理學突破獎。若下屆未得獎，每名物理前沿奖得獎者將會獲30萬美元，並會自動在未來5屆基礎物理學突破獎被提名<ref>{{cite press release |url=https://home.cern/news/press-release/cern/fundamental-physics-prize-foundation-announces-physics-frontiers-and-new |title= Fundamental Physics Prize Foundation announces Physics Frontiers and New Horizons in Physics prizes along with two special prizes |date=2012-12-11 |accessdate=2022-04-30 |publisher=[[歐洲核子研究組織|歐洲核子研究組織]] |location=[[日內瓦|日內瓦]] |archive-date=2022-04-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220430143236/https://home.cern/news/press-release/cern/fundamental-physics-prize-foundation-announces-physics-frontiers-and-new |language=en}}</ref>。

